text:
The room is very small. One needs to climb over the other person in the bed;
In the bathroom, there is no place to put any toiletries;
Why don't they even have a full length mirror in this room? People going out would like to see how they look before leaving;
The breakfast area is so small. Had to wait before there was was an available table;
There could also be a little more lighting in this room.

I wish I would have booked next door at the Fairfield Inn.

The shower was pretty good, and the breakfast selection was was decent.
